                          <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #444444; font-weight: 300;">Late winter is an ideal time to <strong style="font-weight: 500;">inspect irrigation systems</strong> for potential issues caused by colder weather. Identifying leaks, damaged components, or coverage concerns now helps prevent delays and costly repairs when systems are activated in spring.</p>
                          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #444444; font-weight: 300;">Proactive checks ensure efficient watering and healthier landscapes as the growing season begins.</p>
